    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
