    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really great shape! I\u2019ve taken good care of it over the years, so it\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and is ready for all your upcoming adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s been loved, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
