      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and its signature individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock for precise torque vectoring. This unit has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the internal valvetrain and VANOS system remain within tight tolerances. The chassis utilizes Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to manage rebound and compression, maintaining composure through high-load cornering. While showing minor cosmetic evidence of spirited road use, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are superlative. A turn-key driver's car for the purist who values engineering over aesthetics.",
